data.title: NFR Films by Induction
data.meta_description: All 875 films listed by the year of their induction into the National Film Registry (1989-2023). You can nominate films for future induction here. And be sure to check out this list of eligible films. 1989 The Best Years of Our Lives (1946) Casablanca (1942) [Legacy] Citizen Kane (1941) [Part 2] [Part 3] The Crowdâ€¦
data.text:
I am in no way associated with the National Film Registry, the National Film Preservation Board, the National Film Preservation Foundation, the Library of Congress, the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences, the International House of Pancakes, or any other government agency or film organization. Like so many other Americans, I'm just a guy on the internet who watches movies.

The opinions expressed on this blog are my own and do not reflect those of anyone else, including myself because, honestly, I'm really not paying attention when I write these things.

All links used in these write-ups were verified as working at the time of posting. Links may not work in the future, because even in the future, nothing works.
